'''二甲基砜'''（'''Methylsulfonylmethane''')，簡稱為'''有機硫 (MSM)'''其[[化學式|化學式]]為(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>2</sub>、甲基硫醯基甲烷的[[碸|碸]]類[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.gaylordchemical.com/bulletins/Bulletin301B/Bulletin301B.pdf|title= Various Names for MSM|accessdate= June 8, 2009|deadurl= yes|archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110711080324/http://www.gaylordchemical.com/bulletins/Bulletin301B/Bulletin301B.pdf|archivedate= 2011年7月11日}}</ref>。二甲基砜在常溫下是無色固體，無化學活性。在一些植物中含有二甲基砜，也出現在許多的食品及飲料中，會稱為[[膳食補充劑|膳食補充劑]]。在海面上方的大氣中也會有二甲基砜，是空氣中[[慢生根瘤菌科|慢生根瘤菌科]]細菌、[[阿菲波菌属|阿菲波菌]]（''[[Afipia|Afipia]]''）的碳的來源<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2013/01/22/1212089110.full.pdf+html|title= Microbiome of the upper troposphere: Species composition and prevalence, effects of tropical storms, and atmospheric implications|author = Natasha DeLeon-Rodriguez, others ([http://www.pnas.org/content/early/2013/01/22/1212089110?tab=author-info full list])|date = December 19, 2012 (received for review July 15, 2012)|quote = This group [Afipia] is commonly found in aquatic environments and is known to use dimethyl sulfone (DMSO<small>2</small>) as a sole carbon source. DMSO<small>2</small> represents an intermediate of the oxidation of dimethyl sulfide (DMS), which is commonly found in the marine atmosphere|accessdate=2014-03-01 |language=en |page=5 }}</ref>，也曾在人體的黑色素瘤细胞发现過<ref name=sfc>{{cite web |title=Sniffing for Cancer |url=http://theinstitute.ieee.org/technology-focus/technology-topic/sniffing-for-cancer |publisher=Institute for Electrical and Electronic Engineers |date=2013-12-20 |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006171135/http://theinstitute.ieee.org/technology-focus/technology-topic/sniffing-for-cancer |archivedate=2016-10-06 |access-date=2014-05-19 }}</ref>。

== 結構和化學性質 ==
二甲基碸和相應的[[二甲基亞砜|二甲基亞砜]]具有不同的物理性質。 二甲基碸在[[标准状况|標準溫度與標準壓力]]下為白色結晶固體（熔點=109℃），而二甲基亞砜是在標準條件下為液體。亞砜是[[极性非质子溶剂|高度極性非質子溶劑]]，可與水混溶；這也是一個很好的配體。二甲基碸比二甲基亞砜反應性較低，因為砜的硫原子已經在其最高氧化狀態。事實上亞砜氧化產生砜，既可在實驗室條件下也可在新陳代謝中。

== 合成 ==
二甲基砜可以通過與過氧化氫，二甲基硫的氧化來製備。 二甲基亞砜可作為(可分離)中間體。
